A vast desert landscape littered with countless abandoned wooden market stalls and kiosks stretching to the horizon, their faded canopies flapping in the wind, tumbleweeds rolling through empty aisles, a single vulture perched on a crooked "For Rent" sign post, golden hour lighting casting long shadows across the dusty ground, photorealistic style with cinematic composition, muted earth tones with occasional pops of sun-bleached color on weathered fabrics, conveying themes of failed commerce and digital ghost towns
